		"Name": "Charger",
		"Details": "The Charger, an oft maligned mech, is one of those chassis that seem to show up whenever someone needs a mech.   Periphery Armaments, knowing full well of this 'availability factor' jumped at the chance to make their own mark on the Charger lineage.   Knowing full well that periphery powers would need a low cost mech, PAI focused on in-expensive reliable weaponry.   Knowing the Charger was noted for high speed, meant Prototype XL and Prototype Endosteel were required to free up valuable tonnage.  The PAR1 Charger CGR-1PAR1 was born of this confluence of expensive internal components, cheap and reliable weapons, and 19.5 tons of Face Hardened Grade B Heavy Plate armor    The 1PAR1 Charger is Fast, Heavy and moderately armed with a Howitzer 8 (3 tons of ammo) 2 Medium ChemPulse Lasers and a Large ChemLaser (3 tons of Ammo again.)",
